    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Coalition Government is committed to publishing departmental spend over £25,000 as part of its commitment to transparency and open government.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is the Foreign Office spend in the UK for transactions totalling over £25,000 published by month. We have published our spend in line with Cabinet Office guidelines which allow for data protection of individuals and security constraints.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
