    <title>Exceptions data</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;The coalition government has put in place measures to constrain spending. Government departments have been asked to limit their expenditure in five areas. These are:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Consultancy&lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;ICT &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Recruitment of certain new staff &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Marketing &lt;/li&gt;
  &lt;li&gt;Property&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;p&gt;Foreign &amp;amp; Commonwealth Office (FCO) exceptions to each of the moratorium listed are published here.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
